  | date = 25 May 2008
| url = https://www.pbs.org/memorialdayconcert/concert/performers.html#sarah
  | access-date =26 May 2008 }}</ref> Brightman made her feature film debut as Blind Mag in the [[rock musical]] film ''[[Repo! The Genetic Opera]]'' which was released on 7 November 2008.<ref name="CNN001">
{{cite news
